A game-changing moment emerged in 2008 when India's Chandrayaan-1 mission unveiled an astonishing find: water on the moon's surface. snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 Landing Live: ISRO's Chandrayaan-3 Mission Vikram rover soft landing on Moon
snippet.description:
#chandrayaan3 #chandrayaan3landing #isro 
 
भारतीय अंतरिक्ष एजेंसी (ISRO) द्वारा निर्मित चंद्रयान-3 के विक्रम लूनर रोवर के चंद्रमा की सतह पर बुधवार को सफलतापूर्वक उतर गया। भारत दुनिया का पहला देश है जिसने चंद्रमा के दक्षिण ध्रुव पर लूनर रोवर भेजने में सफलता प्राप्त की है। इस अवसर पर पीएण नरेन्द्र मोदी ने इसरो के वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों को  सम्बोधित करते हुए कहा, " जब हम अपनी आंखों के सामने ऐसा इतिहास बनते हुए देखते हैं, तो जीवन धन्य हो जाता है। ऐसी ऐतिहासिक घटनाएं, राष्ट्र जीवन की चिरिंजीव चेतना बन जाती हैं। ये पल अविस्मरणीय है। ये क्षण अभूतपूर्व है। ये क्षण, विकसित भारत के शंखनाद का है। ये क्षण, नए भारत के जयघोष का है। ये क्षण, मुश्किलों के महासागर को पार करने का है। ये क्षण, जीत के चंद्रपथ पर चलने का है। ये क्षण, 140 करोड़ धड़कनों के सामर्थ्य का है। ये क्षण, भारत में नई ऊर्जा, नया विश्वास, नईं चेतना का है। ये क्षण, भारत के उदयीमान भाग्य के आह्वान का है। अमृतकाल की प्रथम प्रभा में सफलता की ये अमृतवर्षा हुई है। हमने धरती पर संकल्प लिया, और चाँद पर उसे साकार किया। और हमारे वैज्ञानिक साथियों ने भी कहा कि India is now on the moon. आज हम अन्तरिक्ष में नए भारत की नई उड़ान के साक्षी बने हैं।"

#चंद्रयान_3 #vikramlander #pmmodi #narendramodi #modi 

पीएम मोदी ने वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों से कहा, "मैं टीम चंद्रयान को, इसरो को और देश के सभी वैज्ञानिकों को जी जान से बहुत-बहुत बधाई देता हूँ, जिन्होंने इस पल के लिए वर्षों तक इतना परिश्रम किया है। उत्साह, उमंग, आनंद और भावुकता से भरे इस अद्भुत पल के लिए मैं 140 करोड़ देशवासियों को भी कोटि-कोटि बधाइयाँ देता हूँ!"

पीएम मोदी ने आगे कहा, "हमारे वैज्ञानिकों के परिश्रम और प्रतिभा से भारत, चंद्रमा के उस दक्षिणी ध्रुव पर पहुंचा है, जहां आज तक दुनिया का कोई भी देश नहीं पहुंच सका है। अब आज के बाद से चाँद से जुड़े मिथक बदल जाएंगे, कथानक भी बदल जाएंगे, और नई पीढ़ी के लिए कहावतें भी बदल जाएंगी। भारत में तो हम सभी लोग धरती को माँ कहते हैं और चाँद को मामा बुलाते हैं। कभी कहा जाता था, चंदा मामा बहुत ‘दूर’ के हैं। अब एक दिन वो भी आएगा जब बच्चे कहा करेंगे- चंदा मामा बस एक ‘टूर’ के हैं।"

Chandrayaan 3 mission robotic lunar rover Vikram landed on the Moon today. Chandrayaan-3 is developed by Indian space Research Organization (ISRO). India's is the world's first country to land moon mission on it's south pole. India became 4th country to land on moon. Chandrayaan-3 mission was launched on July 14 on board launch vehicle MARK-III (LVM-3) rocket.

localized.title: Chandrayaan 3 Landing Live: ISRO's Chandrayaan-3 Mission Vikram rover soft landing on Moon
localized.description:
#chandrayaan3 #chandrayaan3landing #isro 
 
भारतीय अंतरिक्ष एजेंसी (ISRO) द्वारा निर्मित चंद्रयान-3 के विक्रम लूनर रोवर के चंद्रमा की सतह पर बुधवार को सफलतापूर्वक उतर गया। भारत दुनिया का पहला देश है जिसने चंद्रमा के दक्षिण ध्रुव पर लूनर रोवर भेजने में सफलता प्राप्त की है। इस अवसर पर पीएण नरेन्द्र मोदी ने इसरो के वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों को  सम्बोधित करते हुए कहा, " जब हम अपनी आंखों के सामने ऐसा इतिहास बनते हुए देखते हैं, तो जीवन धन्य हो जाता है। ऐसी ऐतिहासिक घटनाएं, राष्ट्र जीवन की चिरिंजीव चेतना बन जाती हैं। ये पल अविस्मरणीय है। ये क्षण अभूतपूर्व है। ये क्षण, विकसित भारत के शंखनाद का है। ये क्षण, नए भारत के जयघोष का है। ये क्षण, मुश्किलों के महासागर को पार करने का है। ये क्षण, जीत के चंद्रपथ पर चलने का है। ये क्षण, 140 करोड़ धड़कनों के सामर्थ्य का है। ये क्षण, भारत में नई ऊर्जा, नया विश्वास, नईं चेतना का है। ये क्षण, भारत के उदयीमान भाग्य के आह्वान का है। अमृतकाल की प्रथम प्रभा में सफलता की ये अमृतवर्षा हुई है। हमने धरती पर संकल्प लिया, और चाँद पर उसे साकार किया। और हमारे वैज्ञानिक साथियों ने भी कहा कि India is now on the moon. आज हम अन्तरिक्ष में नए भारत की नई उड़ान के साक्षी बने हैं।"

#चंद्रयान_3 #vikramlander #pmmodi #narendramodi #modi 

पीएम मोदी ने वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों से कहा, "मैं टीम चंद्रयान को, इसरो को और देश के सभी वैज्ञानिकों को जी जान से बहुत-बहुत बधाई देता हूँ, जिन्होंने इस पल के लिए वर्षों तक इतना परिश्रम किया है। उत्साह, उमंग, आनंद और भावुकता से भरे इस अद्भुत पल के लिए मैं 140 करोड़ देशवासियों को भी कोटि-कोटि बधाइयाँ देता हूँ!"

पीएम मोदी ने आगे कहा, "हमारे वैज्ञानिकों के परिश्रम और प्रतिभा से भारत, चंद्रमा के उस दक्षिणी ध्रुव पर पहुंचा है, जहां आज तक दुनिया का कोई भी देश नहीं पहुंच सका है। अब आज के बाद से चाँद से जुड़े मिथक बदल जाएंगे, कथानक भी बदल जाएंगे, और नई पीढ़ी के लिए कहावतें भी बदल जाएंगी। भारत में तो हम सभी लोग धरती को माँ कहते हैं और चाँद को मामा बुलाते हैं। कभी कहा जाता था, चंदा मामा बहुत ‘दूर’ के हैं। अब एक दिन वो भी आएगा जब बच्चे कहा करेंगे- चंदा मामा बस एक ‘टूर’ के हैं।"

Chandrayaan 3 mission robotic lunar rover Vikram landed on the Moon today. Chandrayaan-3 is developed by Indian space Research Organization (ISRO). India's is the world's first country to land moon mission on it's south pole. India became 4th country to land on moon. Chandrayaan-3 mission was launched on July 14 on board launch vehicle MARK-III (LVM-3) rocket.

As the wrestling community grapples with this heartbreak, it's important to remember Bray Wyatt's contributions to the sport. snippet.title: Video of Pragyan Rover Touchdown on Moon | Released by ISRO | చందమామపై ప్రగ్యాన్‌ రోవర్‌ వీడియో
snippet.description:
జాబిల్లి దక్షిణ ధ్రువం సమీపంలో చంద్రయాన్ -3 సురక్షితంగా దిగడంతో అంతరిక్ష రంగంలో భారత్  సరికొత్త చరిత్రను లిఖించగా...చంద్రుడి ఉపరితలంపై ప్రగ్యాన్  రోవర్  అడుగుపెట్టిన వీడియోను ఇస్రో  తాజాగా సామాజిక మాధ్యమం Xలో పంచుకుంది. విక్రమ్  ల్యాండర్  చంద్రుడిపై కాలుమోపిన కొన్ని గంటలకు ప్రగ్యాన్  రోవర్  బయటకు వచ్చింది. చంద్రయాన్ -3 మిషన్ లోని అన్ని వ్యవస్థలూ సక్రమంగానే పనిచేస్తున్నట్లు ఇస్రో స్పష్టం చేసింది..

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3859 | 25 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3859: Dr Hathi Ki Talaash
--------------------------------------------------------
Danger Bhai arrives in Gokuldham and questions the residents about the whereabouts of his brother. The arrival of such a goon frightens everyone in Gokuldham. Danger Bhai's associates question Bhide since he is the secretary of the society. Danger Bhai seeks Dr. Hathi so feverishly to avenge his brother Chintamani's condition that he misses him. Sodhi becomes enraged and lashes out, but Danger Bhai traps him with a tire. How will the people of Gokuldham deal with this chaos? Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3859, 25 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Magnus Carlsen made a very solid draw against Rameshbabu Praggnanandhaa with the White pieces. Pragg did not face any troubles with Black - the players agreed to a draw after 30 moves of play in an equal Bishop ending.

Since the scores are 1-1 after the 2 classical games, we are going into tiebreaks tomorrow! Who do you think has better chances in the tiebreaks?

snippet.title: India Moon landing: Chandrayaan-3 spacecraft lands near south pole - BBC News
snippet.description:
India has made history as its Moon mission becomes the first to land in the lunar south pole region.

With this, India joins an elite club of countries to achieve a soft landing on the Moon, after the US, the former Soviet Union and China.

The Vikram lander from Chandrayaan-3 successfully touched down as planned at 18:04 local time (12:34 GMT).

Celebrations have broken out across the country, with Prime Minister Narendra Modi saying "India is now on the Moon".

snippet.title: CROWN | Introduction | New Life Album | King
snippet.description:
#CROWN #KING #NEWLIFE

“New Life” marks a new era in KING’s career. And “Crown” arrives as the foreword to his upcoming project, and reflects KING’s willingness to address his meteoric rise and the burden of expectations. Beyond standing out as a grand sonic highlight for the soundscapes of his upcoming body of work, the song's energy and intensity align with his relentless knack to experiment with his musical style as an industrial-focused production comes into the foray, and highlights the raw and introspective nature of his lyrical play, while announcing his stake to the ‘Crown’ and fortify his position as India’s quintessential new-age popstar.

STREAM NOW : https://out-now.lnk.to/CROWN

Song Name : CROWN
Artist: KING, Natania
Lyrics : KING, David Arkwright, Natania Lalwani, Miranda Glory
Music Producer : David Arkwright
Composed by : KING, David Arkwright, Natania Lalwani, Miranda Glory
Additional Guitars : Dan Thomas
Recording Engineers : Samir Dharap at Studio 504, Abhishek Khandelwal at YRF Studios
Mix & Master By : Hanish Taneja at Studio Alika
Artwork : Adi Murthi & Ashish Diyali

Concept by X Miikey and KING
Director : Bijoy Shetty (@whatsabijoy)

Action Director : Chand Khan

Post Production House : Trinity Entertainment
Post Producer : Amey Golatkar
Editors : Mehran

VFX Additional Team : Nayanesh Khanvilkar
Grade : Avinash Shukla

Choreography Assistant : Rishikesh Nalawade

Special Appearance by Shubhanshu Singh

Styling : SPECIAL THANKS TO CAMPUS SHOES FOR DANCERS FOOTWEAR STYLING
BTS : Tathagat Pant & Kartik Kher

Follow King: 
Spotify : https://lnk.to/KingSpotify 
Apple : https://out-now.lnk.to/KingApple 
YouTube :  https://lnk.to/KingYouTube 
Instagram : https://lnk.to/KingInstagram 
Facebook : https://lnk.to/KingFacebook 
Twitter : https://lnk.to/KingTwitter 
Snapchat : https://lnk.to/KingSnapchat 

Follow WARNER MUSIC INDIA:
Instagram : https://out-now.lnk.to/WMIInstagram 
Facebook : https://out-now.lnk.to/WMIFacebook 
Twitter : https://out-now.lnk.to/WMITwitter 
Snapchat : https://out-now.lnk.to/WMISnapchat

Lyrics : 
They want me to walk on water  
Just to throw me in to sink
Everybody points a finger 
But they don’t really know a thing 
Every story has a critic 
Who never steps into the ring 
Cause nothing’s as heavy,
Nothing sits heavy as the crown on the king

Mujhpe hai
Ye nazrein mujhpe hai
Kya raja hi jiyega banke saari muddatein
Mein mere jaisa ek
Tum bataado kon sa
Jo saamne khada hua
Milega mitti mein
Aankhein bhaari, raatein kaali
Puche kaisi durdasha
Main zinda mein bhi murdon mein bhi
Naam amar hun kar chuka
Chhodh do,
Chhod do meri saansein
Chal padha
Main ruka hua tha jahaase

Reign of the king, Reign of the king
Bend down and kiss on the ring!

Jisne…
Aankh ladaake baer rakha
Paer rakha jab keher macha
Vo apne karam ka raja, baap ghamand karta hua kabhi na thaka,

Dua deti nahi rukti hai maa,
Kitno ki maa ka main jaise beta,
Kitno ka bhai aur kitno ki aankhon mein
Jhaankta firta main apna pata.

Mujhe dhoondhne do ,
Aasmaan ko chumne do!
Aaj khaakh se laakh ka,
Main usi baat ka, jis baat ki shuruaat ka ant mile chaahe na bhi mile
Maine palat diya hai rukh ab itihaas ka

Panne khule, kisne padhe, kuch na dikhe
Hum the chale, raah pe jinke na bande dikhe
Khud hi kiya, pele chale, dekh rahe mujhe dur se!

Ho panja maarke giraadi jisne khwaab ki diwar
Boley tarakki mashook
Kalakaari sachha pyaar

Kehti aankhon mein na jhaanko raja hua baaghi aaj
Haqdaar lene aara apna taaj
Sometimes being late is being right on time.

snippet.title: Manisha Rani on Abhishek Malhan, Elvish Yadav| REACTS to #Abhisha & #Abhiya fan war| Bigg Boss OTT 2
snippet.description:
Manisha Rani, who was a content creator on social media, participated in Salman Khan's Bigg Boss OTT 2 and reached the finale. She emerged as the second runner-up followed by Abhishek Malhan while Elvish Yadav was announced as the winner. After stepping out of the house, the entertainment queen did an exclusive video interview with Pinkvilla, where she reacted to being shamed inside the house, and answered Pooja Bhatt's claims of her not being capable of becoming an actress. Apart from that, Manisha Rani shared her heartfelt feelings about Abhishek Malhan, Elvish Yadav, and Jad Hadid. In addition to the above topics, the Bigg Boss OTT 2 finalist also spoke about #Abhisha and #Abhiya fan wars on Twitter. Watch the entire video.

#manisharani  #biggbossott2  #abhishekmalhan  #elvishyadav  #jiyashankar  #tonisha  #abhisha  #abhiya  #elvisha 

0:00 - What to expect?
0:20 - Introduction
1:01 - On #Tonisha and prank call to Tony Kakkar
1:48 - On which contestants backstabbed her
2:36 - Manisha on #Abhisha and #Abhiya fan war
3:54 - On Abhishek and Jiya's bond
5:12 - Her reaction to Nischay choosing her as 'bhabhi' over Jiya
6:31 - On Pooja Bhatt's claim that Manisha can never be an actress
7:21 - About entering Bigg Boss 17
7:40 - On Elvish Yadav calling her to meet
8:23 - About Elvish Yadav's girlfriend
9:00 - On her hygiene being questioned in the house
10:07 - On being called a male 'attention-seeker'
11:38 - Did she meet Bebika Dhurve outside?
11:45 - Would she want to bury the hatchet with Bebika?
12:03 - Outro

snippet.title: BIOHAZARDS, MARKETING & TRUCK DRIVER | Australia-New Zealand Stories | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua
snippet.description:
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour

Right from causing chaos and a literal biohazard at the NZ airport customs to getting cussed at and scolded by a truck driver in NZ, this video has it all. No doubt NZ is known for adventure! 
Observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in 3 - 4 shows (unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect), it’s a heartfelt account of my debut standup tour of Australia & New Zealand in June 2023. 


Need all your love, appreciation and support. Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #australia #newzealand #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #funny 

Shot by: Yours Truly & Mehtab Singh 
Edited by Gaurav Bhatt (https://www.instagram.com/gauravbhatt101)
Sound Mixed, Mastered and Engineered by: Sreejit Menon (https://www.instagram.com/porcupinesree)
Transcription, thumbnail and subtitles by : Shivansh Anand (https://www.instagram.com/shivansh.mov)
Special Thanks: Varun Chhabra, Mukund Panchal, Punit Raithata, Sourav Bangotra, Simran Singh

snippet.description:

snippet.title: చంద్రునిపైకి చేరిన భారతదేశం, ప్రపంచాన్ని ఆశ్చర్యపరిచిన ప్రత్యేకతలు || India is on the Moon ||
snippet.description:
చంద్రునిపైకి చేరిన భారతదేశం, ప్రపంచాన్ని ఆశ్చర్యపరిచిన ప్రత్యేకతలు || India is on the Moon ||
Chandrayaan-3's Lander Has Touched Down On Moon. Over To Rover Pragyan
Chandrayaan-3 Moon mission: The rover Pragyan will emerge from the lander three-and-a-half hours since lander Vikram touched down on the lunar surface
Chandrayaan-3's Lander Has Touched Down On Moon. Over To Rover Pragyan
Chandrayaan-3: Lander Vikram landed on the Moon today


New Delhi: The lander Vikram of India's Chandrayaan-3 mission has made it to the Moon, marking a historic day for India and the world. In the next few hours, the rover Pragyan will roll out from the lander to carry out is mission.
Here's your 5-point cheatsheet to this big story
Lander Vikram's final touchdown speed was well within its safe limits. Four engines ran initially. Two of them were shut down later, so the touchdown on the lunar surface was powered by two engines.
Lander Vikram kicked up a large cloud of Moon dust when it landed. The dust will not settle down anytime soon due to the extremely weak gravitational force the Moon exerts, but will scatter away on its own momentum.
https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/chandrayaan-3-lander-vikram-on-moon-now-whats-the-next-immediate-steps-5-points-4322607

snippet.title: Chandrayaan-3 : ల్యాండర్‌ను పరీక్షించిన ఈ మట్టి ఆ ఊరిలో తప్ప భారత్‌లో ఇంకెక్కడా దొరకదు | ISRO
snippet.description:
చంద్రయాన్-3 ప్రయోగంలో భాగంగా విక్రమ్ ల్యాండర్, ప్రజ్ఞాన్ రోవర్‌లను పరీక్షించేందుకు అచ్చం చంద్రుడిపై ఉండే మట్టి నమూనా ఇస్రోకు అవసరమైంది. ఆ తరహా మట్టి భారత దేశంలో తమిళనాడులోని నమక్కల్ జిల్లాలో మాత్రమే దొరుకుతుంది. దీని కథ తెలుసుకోవాలంటే మనం కాస్త గతంలోకి వెళ్లాలి. 
#ISRO #Chandrayaan3 #Sriharikota #MoonMission #India 


___________
ఫేస్‌బుక్, ఇన్‌స్టాగ్రామ్, ట్విటర్‌లలో బీబీసీ తెలుగును ఫాలో అవ్వండి.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3858 | 24 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3858: Danger Bhai
--------------------------------------------------------
Sodhi and Popatlal are playing carom at the Gokuldham Club House when other men enter and join in on the fun. During this time, Abdul appears with several boxes of parcels and enters the clubhouse. Bhide observes this and inquires Abdul about the whereabouts of the boxes. Abdul mentions certain Gokuldham residents who want to maintain their additional parcel at the clubhouse, which Bhide fiercely opposes. Later, Chintamani's conversation with the Gokuldham men begins, and everyone becomes concerned about him. Dr. Hathi receives a call from the city hospital informing him that Chintamani has been hospitalized due to illness. What comes next? Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3858, 24 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: What Will Happen If Chandrayaan-3 is Successful
snippet.description:
Angel One Demat Account(Free) - https://tinyurl.com/2f32osnb
For support, WhatsApp 8688962057

Latest news of Chandrayaan-3
Latest video of Chandrayaan-3

Chandrayaan-3 is the third and most recent Indian lunar exploration mission under the Chandrayaan programme of ISRO. Its propulsion module would act like an orbiter. The propulsion module carries the lander and rover configuration until the spacecraft is in a 100-kilometre (62 mi) lunar orbit. The lander and rover are expected to land near the lunar south pole region on 23 August 2023. The powered descent is scheduled for 23 August 2023, around 05:45 pm IST and touchdown is expected on the same day around 06:05 pm IST.

snippet.title: Sundar के मामले में Jetha ने खीचे अपने पैर| Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah|Episode 827| 21 Aug 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Madhavi is shocked when a tiff with Bhide leads Sunder's men to stop the painting work. He calls everyone asking them to reach Jethalal's house quickly. Everyone feels Champak Chacha is not well and rushes to Jethalals house. Bhide discusses the problem with everyone and everyone asks Jethalal to talk to Sundar in this regard. Jethalal shows reluctance at first but then agrees. To everyone's surprise, Sundarlal shows up at Gokuldham Society. Bhide discusses the problem with him but in return gets a lot of shocks himself.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 827
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Clinical Team India Seal Series Win | 2nd T20I | India tour of Ireland | JioCinema
snippet.description:
After being asked to bat first, Ruturaj Gaikwad & Sanju Samson starred for India with impactful innings before Rinku Singh and Shivam Dube blazed away at the end, to take the the team to a score of 185/5.

Ireland, meanwhile, had a difficult start to the run chase after Prasidh Krishna picked up early wickets with his pace. Andy Balbirnie stood tall for the hosts, smashing a valiant 72 before a clinical finish with the ball by Jasprit Bumrah and Arshdeep Singh, secured victory for #TeamIndia by 33 runs and gain an unassailable 2-0 series lead.


Relive the Excitement! Highlights of 2nd T20I | India vs. Ireland | 20th August 2023. 

Don't miss a single moment of the action as India takes on Ireland in the first thrilling T20I match of the series.

Episode 90: Virus Phel Gaya
-------------------------------------------------
Aageel and Shashmaag invent a lethal virus that will wipe off humanity forever. Aageel targets a vegetable vendor to inject the virus, allowing this dangerous infection to spread quickly among the large throng. She also tries to keep a bunch of kids playing on the ground under control, but Baalveer comes just in time and destroys the virus. When Shashmaag sees this, he becomes enraged, but Aageel assures him that the virus is safe and that she staged the entire event to keep the truth from Baalveer. Sirf Tum Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 24th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

snippet.title: இறுதி கட்டத்தில் இஸ்ரோவின் Plan-B என்ன? | Chandrayaan-3 | Mr.GK
snippet.description:
1. *Plan A:* சரியான Orbit லேயே இயக்கிக்கொண்டு Lander - ஐ தரை இறக்குவது.

*Plan B:* Orbit - ல் சிறிது மாற்றம் அடைந்தாலும் அதை தானாக சீர் செய்து தரை இறங்க முயல்வது.

2. *Plan A:* Solar panel மூலமாக Power - செய்து Lander இயங்கும்.

*Plan B :* ஒரு வேளை அது தடை பட்டால், Extra battery  மூலமாக தடை இல்லாமல் இயங்க வைப்பது.

3. *Plan A :* Lander -ல் உள்ள 4 thrusters - ஐ பயன்படுத்தி தரை இறங்குவது.

*Plan B:* Lander - ல் உள்ள இரண்டு thrusters - ஐ மற்றும் பயன்படுத்தி பாதுகாப்பாக தரை இறங்குவது. 

4. *Plan A:* Fix செய்யப்பட்ட Target location - ல் தரை இறங்குவது.

*Plan B:* அங்கு எதாவது பிரச்சனை இருந்தால் fix செய்யப்பட்ட 2.5 km * 4. 5 km பரப்பளவில் எங்கு வேண்டுமானாலும் தரை இறங்குவது.

snippet.title: Rebel Moon | Official Teaser Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
A new universe awaits on Netflix, starting December 22.

From Zack Snyder, the filmmaker behind 300, Man of Steel, and Army of the Dead, comes REBEL MOON, an epic science-fantasy event decades in the making.

When a peaceful colony on the edge of a galaxy finds itself threatened by the armies of a tyrannical ruling force, Kora (Sofia Boutella), a mysterious stranger living among the villagers, becomes their best hope for survival.

Tasked with finding trained fighters who will unite with her in making an impossible stand against the Mother World, Kora assembles a small band of warriors — outsiders, insurgents, peasants and orphans of war from different worlds who share a common need for redemption and revenge.

As the shadow of an entire Realm bears down on the unlikeliest of moons, a battle over the fate of a galaxy is waged, and in the process, a new army of heroes is formed.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 238 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Rebel Moon | Official Teaser Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

snippet.title: Sirf Tum Episode 44 Teaser - 24th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 44 Teaser - 24th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Directed by: Mazhar Moin

snippet.title: Rover Pragyan Rolls Out Of Chandrayaan-3 Lander Near Moon's South Pole
snippet.description:
Chandrayaan 3 Updates: India's moon mission Chandrayaan-3 made a perfect landing today near the South Pole of the moon. The next big manoeuvre was the rolling out of the Pragyan rover, which will send data from the spot to the lander that will be relayed to space agency ISRO.  The launch of the rover, though, took time. This is because the rover cannot be launched till the dust kicked up by the touchdown of the Vikram lander is dissipated. The gravity of moon being a fraction of that of Earth, dust does not settle the way it does on Earth.

Sirf Tum Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 23rd Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?
